@page
@model CarCollection.Pages.Customer.Home.IndexModel
@{ViewData["Title"] = "Index";}
<section id="title">

    <img class="rounded mx-auto d-block" src="~/images/Title2.png" />
</section>
<section id="slideshow">

    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 600px !important">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100 h-100" src="/images/banner1.jpg" alt="First slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 h-100" src="/images/banner2.jpg" alt="Second slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 h-100" src="/images/banner3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 h-100" src="/images/banner4.jpg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
<div id="mainDiv">
    <h1 class="text-center">Lillywhite Rentals - My Collection</h1>
    <p class="text-justify" style=" margin-left: 15%; margin-right: 15%; margin-bottom: 25px;"> 
    The Lillywhite Rentals web application is a demonsration website that makes use of the repository pattern. 
    The Website utilizes 3rd party APIs in order to achieve common tasks in the form of managing user logins and formatting user inputted text. The Website both pushes and pulls
    from a remote database where it stores information about car rental reviews that users can create. The User is able to create reviews which allow for image file uploads to the server.
    The user can also edit and delete their own created reviews. Users can browse other users' reviews. They can search, sort, and filter through reviews as needed via a paginated DataTable.
    Admins can edit the remote database's various tables through the web application. The Admin can create other accounts and give them authorization to different functionality on the website.
    </p>
    @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
    {
        <hr />
        <h1>
            Hello, @Model.DemoVar
        </h1>
        <hr />
    }
    <div class="panel-group text-center" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title" id="accordion-panel-title">
                    <span data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1" id="accordion-title">
                        Browse Reviews
                    </span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <div style=" width: 100%; margin: auto; padding: 20px;">
                        <table id="DT_load" class="table table-striped table-bordered" style="width:100%;">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="width: 50%;">
                                        Car Image
                                    </th>
                                    <th style="width: 15%;">
                                        Car
                                    </th>
                                    <th style="width: 5%;">
                                        Rating
                                    </th>
                                    <th style="width: 20%;">
                                        Author
                                    </th>
                                    <th style="width: 10%;">
                                        <!-- Buttons Column -->
                                    </th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @section Scripts
    {
        <script src="~/js/collection.js"></script>
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function () {
                var toggleVar = false;
                $('#accordion-title').click(function (e) {
                    if (toggleVar == false) {
                        $('#accordion-title').css("background-color", "#001a0e");
                        $('#accordion-title').text("Hide Reviews");
                        toggleVar = true;
                    }
                    else {
                        toggleVar = false;
                        $('#accordion-title').css("background-color", "#004225");
                        $('#accordion-title').text("Browse Reviews");
                    }
                });
            });
        </script>
    }
</div>
